LONDON, ENGLAND- Adam Benigni reports from London England that Bills quarterback Tyrod Taylor is making progress in his recovery from a knee injury. 
There's a chance that Taylor could be healthy enough to start Sunday's game against the Jaguars. Read or Share this story: http://on.wgrz.com/1LNs6rc More Stories
